AI for Computational Engineering: Key Papers
Machine Learning for Simulation & PDEs

Learning mesh-based simulation with graph networks
Multiscale meshgraphnets (Fortunato et al., 2022)
Transolver: A fast transformer solver for PDEs on general geometries (Wu et al., 2024)
PIGNN-CFD: A physics-informed graph neural network for rapid predicting urban wind field defined on unstructured mesh (Shao et al., 2023)
Hood: Hierarchical graphs for generalized modelling of clothing dynamics (Grigorev et al., 2023)
Geometry-informed neural operator for large-scale 3D PDEs (Li et al., 2023)
PhyCRNet: Physics-informed convolutional-recurrent network for solving spatiotemporal PDEs (Ren et al., 2022)
Physics-informed graph neural Galerkin networks: A unified framework for solving PDE-governed forward and inverse problems (Gao et al., 2022)

Physics-Informed AI

Physics-informed machine learning: A survey on problems, methods and applications (Hao et al., 2022)
When physics meets machine learning: A survey of physics-informed machine learning (Meng et al., 2022)
A physics-informed diffusion model for high-fidelity flow field reconstruction (Shu et al., 2023)
Clifford neural layers for PDE modeling (Brandstetter et al., 2022)
Physics-informed PointNet: A deep learning solver for steady-state incompressible flows and thermal fields on multiple sets of irregular geometries (Kashefi & Mukerji, 2022)
Super-resolution and denoising of fluid flow using physics-informed convolutional neural networks without high-resolution labels (Gao et al., 2021)

Deep Learning in Materials & Design

Artificial intelligence for science in quantum, atomistic, and continuum systems (Zhang et al., 2023)
Accelerating the design of compositionally complex materials via physics-informed artificial intelligence (Raabe et al., 2023)
Deep generative models in engineering design: A review (Regenwetter et al., 2022)
Pre-training via denoising for molecular property prediction (Zaidi et al., 2022)
Predicting stress, strain and deformation fields in materials and structures with graph neural networks (Maurizi et al., 2022)
A state-of-the-art review on machine learning-based multiscale modeling, simulation, homogenization and design of materials (Bishara et al., 2023)

Graph Neural Networks for Engineering

Towards high-accuracy axial springback: Mesh-based simulation of metal tube bending via geometry/process-integrated graph neural networks (Wang et al., 2024)
Graph neural networks for temporal graphs: State of the art, open challenges, and opportunities (Longa et al., 2023)
Towards understanding generalization of graph neural networks (Tang & Liu, 2023)
Towards multi-spatiotemporal-scale generalized PDE modeling (Gupta & Brandstetter, 2022)
DyGFormer: A new Transformer-based architecture for dynamic graph learning (Yu et al., 2023)
Combinatorial optimization and reasoning with graph neural networks (Cappart et al., 2023)

Advanced ML for Engineering Applications

Learning dynamical systems from data: An introduction to physics-guided deep learning (Yu & Wang, 2024)
Multiple physics pretraining for physical surrogate models (McCabe et al., 2023)
Deep learning in computational mechanics: A review (Herrmann & Kollmannsberger, 2024)
Machine learning with data assimilation and uncertainty quantification for dynamical systems: A review (Cheng et al., 2023)
Learning multi-object dynamics with compositional neural radiance fields (Driess et al., 2023)
Current and emerging deep-learning methods for the simulation of fluid dynamics (Lino et al., 2023)
Deep learning methods for flood mapping: A review of existing applications and future research directions (Bentivoglio et al., 2022)
Continuous PDE dynamics forecasting with implicit neural representations (Yin et al., 2022)

Energy Management & Data Centers

Deep learning GAN-based data generation and fault diagnosis in the data center HVAC system (Du et al., 2023)
Evaporative cooling method to improve energy management of overhead downward flow-type data center (Lee et al., 2023)
DRL-S: Toward safe real-world learning of dynamic thermal management in data center (Zhang et al., 2023)
Optimization air-conditioning system and thermal management of data center via fan-wall free cooling technology (Zhang et al., 2023)

